title: 2nd Made for Good Startup-Market on November 22 / 23 at Deutsche Bank
body:
Come to the 2nd Made for Good Startup-Market on November 22 and 23 at Deutsche Bank in Frankfurt, Taunusanlage 12.
Thirteen exciting social startups present their ideas and sell products with added value. The market is open to the public. We are looking forward to seeing you there!
These startups take part:
